### Check Email Verification Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/check-verification?email=test@example.com
Content-Type: application/json

### Resend Verification Email
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Verify Email with Token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/verify-email?token_hash=your_token_hash&type=signup
Content-Type: application/json 